0Z","msg":"一世都唔會"},{"pid":"423d221c63bfced71cce2b112f1481ac52637f8d","tid":1477031,"uid":81183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:10:07.000Z","msg":"全部黑警舌槍自殺加捐晒身家出黎比義士我就原諒佢d家屬"},{"pid":"bbdfeb0fe8e66118e62e3b93c43fc464b0ac8aa9","tid":1477031,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"原佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b7b79ab66e6e24976edb2f8fb23f09476db30772","tid":1477031,"uid":35923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"原唔原諒嘅嘢交返俾上帝決定"},{"pid":"39fad957da88c051e06ab6b8ea04408189a4c92b","tid":1477031,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:11:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSD-Challenge-103297651036526%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=7769e6c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們是一群香港人，熱血自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n我們現正受到中國黨國體系的打壓，我們不希望在銀行的存款成為中資企業的貸款，助紂為虐；我們亦不相信港共政權並沒有透過外匯基金持有大量人民幣資產。<br />\n<br />\n對於一個連市民性命安危都無法保障的政府，我們不認為他們有能力捍衛龐大的聯繫匯率制度。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我們發起USD Challenge。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n「接受挑戰者，請到銀行或找換店換取至少1000蚊美元現鈔，拍照上傳至社交媒體，同時附上此段文字並標籤三名好友，向他們發起挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hongkongers embracing freedom and democracy.<br />\n<br />\nWe are currently oppressed by the China party state system. We don&rsquo;t want our deposits in bank becomes loans for Chinese enterprises. Such action is assisting tyrant to act brutally. Also, we don&rsquo;t believe that the communist regime in Hong Kong doesn&rsquo;t hold large portion of RMB assets through Exchange Funds. <br />\n<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t think that the Government is able to defend the huge Linked Exchange Rate System because the Government cannot even protect citizens&rsquo; lives.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, we launch USD Challenge.<br />\n<br />\nThe flow is as followed:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To those who accept the challenge, please go to banks or exchange stores, get at least $1000 USD cash, take a photo and upload to any social media. At the same time, attach this paragraph, tag three friends and challenge them.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"f188187da761eb957ddb002bd12f1e6def86e7e8","tid":1477031,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"咁都要問 都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定唔原諒"},{"pid":"0e82871e132b20fcfff50c7d63213c394fd88262","tid":1477031,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推！推！推！推！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://im5.ezgif.com/tmp/ezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fim5.ezgif.com%2Ftmp%2Fezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif&h=5f074275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">8.16 學界-攬炒聯手萬人集會！國際本土戰線會師！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/D676SeT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD676SeT.png&h=466b07cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/TmWGGaz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTmWGGaz.png&h=463152b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<i